@startuml
[*] --> RegisteredOrLoggedIn
RegisteredOrLoggedIn --> TeacherOrStudent : user logged in as teacher or student
note right of RegisteredOrLoggedIn: user can continue as teacher or student after logging in
TeacherOrStudent --> CreateQuiz : teacher creates new quiz
CreateQuiz --> EditExistingQuiz : teacher edits existing quiz
EditExistingQuiz --> SaveDraftOrPost : teacher saves quiz as draft or posts it for students
SaveDraftOrPost --> ViewResults : teacher views quiz results once the quiz is over
note right of SaveDraftOrPost: teacher can save quiz as draft or post it for students
StudentSelectsQuiz --> AnswerSelectedQuiz : student answers selected quiz
AnswerSelectedQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : student submits quiz after answering
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult : student views result after submitting quiz
@enduml
